Package: pakscape
Version: @VERSION@
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCHITECTURE@
Maintainer: PakScape contributors <timbergeron@users.noreply.github.com>
Installed-Size: @INSTALLED_SIZE@
Depends: ca-certificates, libc6 (>= 2.38), libgcc-s1, libgssapi-krb5-2, libicu74 | libicu76 | libicu78, libssl3t64, libstdc++6, tzdata, zlib1g, libx11-6, libice6, libsm6, libfontconfig1, mpv, xdg-utils
Homepage: https://github.com/timbergeron/PakScape
Description: Quake PAK and PK3 archive browser and editor
 PakScape provides folder navigation, search, drag-and-drop import,
 archive editing, safe export, and desktop file associations for Quake
 PAK and PK3 archives.
